widevin uses a minimal Prost schema derived from Devin/Cascade protocol
`.proto` files vendored in the repository from:

https://github.com/can1357/oh-my-pi

Upstream snapshot path:

packages/ai/src/providers/devin/proto

The definitions in `rust/src/proto.rs` reproduce only the field numbers and
wire types needed by this crate. They are included for protocol
interoperability, and consumers do not need `protoc` or Buf.
